joining as a curve and only descending half-way; alpha is broad with straight bar, in one case slightly curved with the apex extending at the top; nu has shorter right vertical joining the diagonal above the line; omicron is small and mid-line.",[49,55],{"type":50,"l":51,"from":52,"to":52,"h":53,"unit":54,"atLeast":53,"atMost":53},"letterHeight","Line 1","line1","30","mm",{"type":56,"l":57,"from":52,"to":58,"h":59,"unit":54},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","line2","NA",{"_":61,"notBefore":62,"notAfter":63,"evidence":64},"The tomb has not been excavated fully, but the cemetery went out of use around the end of the 3rd century BCE or early 2nd century, offering a terminus ante quem",-350,-201,"archaeological-context",[66,72],{"_":67,"type":68,"ref":69,"corresp":70,"region":71},"Abacaenum","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462062","#findspot","Sicilia",{"_":8,"type":73,"ref":74,"offset":75,"region":71},"modern","http://sws.geonames.org/2522853","near",[77],[78,79],38.05191,15.10158,[13,14],"Sicily",{"_":4,"role":3,"ref":5},{"type":84},"inventory",{"_":86,"mainLang":87,"languages":88},"Ancient Greek","grc",[86],{"n":90,"url":91,"height":92,"width":93,"desc":94,"surfaceType":95},"screen","ISic004415_tiled.tif","3680px","5520px","I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana","front",[97],{"atLeast":98,"atMost":98},30,[100,101],"Bacci, Coppolino, 2009, La Necropoli di Abakainon: primi dati","Sofia, 2018, Nuove iscrizioni funerarie dalla necropoli di Abakainon",[103,104],"DX8AWC9Q","JQQKI6JP",[106,107,108,26,30,34,109,110,111,112,110,113,114,87],"isic004415","epitaph for krimma, child of aunakos",{"_":23},"abacaenum","tripi","sicilia","sicily","necropoli di abakainon","ancient greek","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan